<br>
Is this a spell you other 50+ folk expect your cleric to give you or in special conditions?  Is the success rate worth the effort/buff slot.<br>
<br>
I find I don't die that often on raids and such. If I die while 2 boxing I am usually OOM and pet is dead so I'm not sure that popping back when I have hit jboots on cleric and headed for zone will be all that helpfull <p><center>
